'''BMW X4'''是[[德國|德國]]汽車公司[[BMW|BMW]]生產的一款高級緊湊型跨界[[SUV|SUV]]，發布於2014年。BMW X4生產於[[美國|美國]][[南卡羅來納州|南卡羅來納州]][[格里爾_(南卡羅來納州)|格里爾]]的工程。BMW X4的概念車在2013年發布<ref name=press>{{cite press release |author=<!--Staff writer(s); no by-line.--> |title=BMW at Auto Shanghai 2013. |url=https://www.press.bmwgroup.com/pressclub/p/pcgl/pressDetail.html?title=bmw-at-auto-shanghai-2013&outputChannelId=6&id=T0138878EN&left_menu_item=node__2318 |publisher=BMW |date=4 May 2013 |accessdate=2013-11-13 |archive-date=2013-11-13 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20131113190453/https://www.press.bmwgroup.com/pressclub/p/pcgl/pressDetail.html?title=bmw-at-auto-shanghai-2013&outputChannelId=6&id=T0138878EN&left_menu_item=node__2318 |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{Cite web |url=http://www.autoblog.com/2013/04/04/bmw-x4-concept-shanghai-photos-reveal/ |title=BMW X4 Concept is no Shanghai surprise |accessdate=2016-01-18 |archive-date=2015-09-24 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150924052233/http://www.autoblog.com/2013/04/04/bmw-x4-concept-shanghai-photos-reveal/ |dead-url=no }}</ref>，並在2014年的紐約車展上正式亮相<ref>{{Cite web |url=https://www.press.bmwgroup.com/global/pressDetail.html?title=bmw-at-the-114th-new-york-international-auto-show-2014&outputChannelId=6&id=T0172307EN&left_menu_item=node__8977 |title=BMW at the 114th New York International Auto Show 2014. |accessdate=2016-01-18 |archive-date=2015-07-24 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150724054346/https://www.press.bmwgroup.com/global/pressDetail.html?title=bmw-at-the-114th-new-york-international-auto-show-2014&outputChannelId=6&id=T0172307EN&left_menu_item=node__8977 |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{Cite web |url=http://www.autoblog.com/2014/04/16/2015-bmw-x4-new-york-2014/ |title=2015 BMW X4 is a budget X6 |accessdate=2016-01-18 |archive-date=2015-09-24 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150924110052/http://www.autoblog.com/2014/04/16/2015-bmw-x4-new-york-2014/ |dead-url=no }}</ref>，在2014年春季開始發售。

